it.emarolab.sit.sceneRepresentation

Class SpatialRelation

  • java.lang.Object
    • it.emarolab.sit.sceneRepresentation.SpatialRelation
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    SITBase

    public class SpatialRelation
extends java.lang.Object
implements SITBase
    The container for a spatial relation between two objects.

    This class is a simple container for relate two SpatialAtom (i.e.: subject and object) within a spatial relation obtained from the ontology through SWRL rules. Rules are evaluated between al pairs of individuals in the CLASS#PRIMITIVE, remember that those are computationally expensive and so the number of individual in such a class should be as small as possible. Also they assume that all the individuals have all the numbers describing their coefficients.
